1. SOFTWARE  —  licensed GPL-2.0 (see LICENSE)
   ------------------------------------------------------------------------
   The web application under web/ (HTML, CSS, JavaScript), the build scripts
   under build/, and the arrangement of the bundled data.

   The rules automation is a clean-room reimplementation in JavaScript of the
   game rules, using Jonathan Mann's "Java Fabled Lands" (JaFL) as the
   reference specification. JaFL is published on SourceForge
   (https://sourceforge.net/projects/flapp/) under GPL-2.0, and the section
   data files under books/ were obtained from that project. Because JaFL is
   distributed as GPL version 2 (with no "or later" clause), this project is
   licensed GPL-2.0 to remain compatible with the material it reuses.

